data.description:
Exceptional location, safe neighborhood, central heat and air, all new restroom fixtures, newly built second restroom, Kitchen new counter tops, new stove stop, dishwasher, washer and dryer, refrigerator all included. Very well kept hardwood floors, newly redone driveway fits four cars, handmade wooden doghouse built in the backyard. New backyard fence. Just five minutes from Texas Tech university, Hutch middle school, Roscoe Wilson elementary Just a short walk to J&B coffee shop and new Brewery as well as Food King grocery store. Also located short walk to Wagner Park and also Tech Terrace Park in the immediate area, city bus stop, available one house down at stop sign. House is not furnished with furniture just major appliances.

First month's rent due as well as security deposit due at signing, Renters are responsible for all utilities, pets allowed
